ZH: 假如我有时间，我将去参加聚会。
EN: If I have time, I will attend the gathering.

ZH: 假如明天下雨，我们就取消野餐。
EN: If it rains tomorrow, we will cancel the picnic.

ZH: 假如你坚持这种做法，你可能会失败。
EN: If you insist on this approach, you might fail.

ZH: 假如你不紧急，我可以帮你办这件事。
EN: If you're not in a hurry, I can help you with this matter.

ZH: 假如我有更多钱，我会买辆新车。
EN: If I have more money, I will buy a new car.

ZH: 假如他不努力学习，他无法通过考试。
EN: If he doesn't study hard, he won't be able to pass the exam.

ZH: 假如你请我到你家，我肯定会前去。
EN: If you invite me to your house, I will definitely come.

ZH: 假如你愿意等一下，我去给你带回来。
EN: If you're willing to wait for a moment, I'll go and bring it back for you.

ZH: 假如他明天能来，我们可以一起去看电影。
EN: If he can come tomorrow, we can go watch a movie together.

ZH: 假如你持续下去，你将获得成功。
EN: If you keep going, you will achieve success.

ZH: 假如你早点告诉我，我会考虑帮助你的。
EN: If you had told me earlier, I would have considered helping you.

ZH: 假如你不犯错误，你就不会从中学到经验。
EN: If you don't make mistakes, you won't learn from them.

ZH: 假如我们错过火车，我们将乘下一班。
EN: If we miss the train, we will take the next one.

ZH: 假如我得到这份工作，我将全力以赴。
EN: If I get this job, I will give it my all.

ZH: 假如你不听我的劝告，你可能会后悔。
EN: If you don't listen to my advice, you might regret it.

ZH: 假如你好好学习，你将取得好成绩。
EN: If you study hard, you will achieve good grades.

ZH: 假如你喜欢旅行，你应该去探索世界各地。
EN: If you enjoy traveling, you should explore different parts of the world.

ZH: 假如你尽快完成任务，你将获得奖励。
EN: If you complete the task as soon as possible, you will be rewarded.

ZH: 假如你对他更友好，他可能会对你更好。
EN: If you are friendlier to him, he might be nicer to you.

ZH: 假如你没问题的话，我们可以开始工作了。
EN: If you're ready, we can start working now.
